## 1. Introduction

### 1.1 Purpose

This FSD specifies the functional behavior of the Injector module within the Kiro SDLC Agent VS Code extension.

### 1.2 Scope

1. injectAll() — Copy all core components + one indexer language
2. injectSelective() — QuickPick UI for user to choose components
3. copyDirRecursive() / copyFiltered() — Low-level copy utilities
4. checkStatus() — Report which components exist

