### 3.3 Recursive Directory Copy (UC-3)

Exclusion list: node\_modules, **pycache**, .git, out, dist Business Rules: BR-8 to BR-11

### 3.4 Filtered Copy for Indexer (UC-4)

Business Rules: BR-12 to BR-15

### 3.5 Check Component Status (UC-5)

Business Rules: BR-16, BR-17

